Action #3: Send email — Action needed (If yes branch)
Steps:

Inside the If yes branch of Any CAPs missing BU?, click Add an action
Search for Send an email (V2) — under the Office 365 Outlook connector → select it
Rename the action to Email - Action needed
Configure these fields:

To: your email address (just type it in)
Subject:
[Action Needed] CAP to BU Mapping — @{length(body('Get_CAPs_missing_BU')?['value'])} item(s) missing BU
This puts the count of missing items directly in the subject line.
